<div class="column">
  <div class="ui two cards">
    <div class="ui card">
      <div class="content">
        <div class="center aligned header"><i class="green big money bill alternate outline icon"></i>Agent Income</div>
        <div class="center aligned description">
          <p>According to NAR, the median gross income of REALTORSÂ® was $42,500 in 2018. </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="ui card">
      <div class="content">
        <div class="ui center aligned header">Your results</div>
        <div class="ui center green aligned big header ">79%</div>
        <div class="center aligned description">
          <p><i class="green dollar circle icon"></i>Congratulations! Based on your goals, you are above average! To achieve that you will need to sell or buy X homes.  That's X per quarter.  (if above the Income goal is above $42,500)</p>
          <p><i class="green dollar circle icon"></i>Real Estate is a great part time income.  Based on your goals, you will need to sell or buy X homes.  That's X per quarter.  (SurveyResult::WORKLOADS = ["20 to 35 hours per week" OR  "Less than 20 per week"]) </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="column">
  <%= simple_form_for(
    @survey_result,
    url: public_survey_results_path,
    method: :post,
    html: { data: { behavior: "agent-assessment-form", fv_live: "enabled" } }
  ) do |f| %>
    <div class="ui segment tab transition fade in active" id="current-year-progress" data-tab="current-year-progress">
      <h4 class="ui dividing header">Current Pipeline</h4>
      <%= f.input(
        :current_ytd_income,
        label: "What is your income YTD (on closed business)? " ,
        as: :currency
      ) %>
      <%= f.input(
        :current_ytd_lead_count,
        label: "How many leads do you currently have (that are not yet clients)? "
      ) %>
      <%= f.input(
        :current_ytd_client_count,
        label: "How many clients do you currently have (that are not closed yet)?"
      ) %>
      <div class="ui primary icon button" data-tab-open="goal-setting">Back</div>
      <%= f.button(
        :submit,
        value:  "Submit",
        class: "ui primary submit button",
        disable_with: "Submiting..."
      ) %>

    </div>
  <% end %>
</div><!-- /.column -->

